1 (2) If the published loan value exceeds the invoiced price, the
2 taxpayer shall establish to the secretary's satisfaction that the price
3 reflected on the invoice or other document is true and correct.
4 (3) If the secretary determines that the invoiced price is not
5 the actual selling price of the motorboat, the total consideration shall be
